page.title: 11HOUSING IN GATLEY.
page.content: THE TYPES OF HOUSING IN OUR AREA ARE MOSTLY SEMI-DETACHED,TERRACED FLATS AND BUNGALOWS. THE AGE OF MY HOUSE IS FIFTY YEARS OLD.IT WAS BUILT IN THE 193O'S.IT IS SITUATED WELL,WE HAVE A FAIRLY BIG BACK GARDEN AND QUITE A SMALL FRONT GARDEN. ON THE WHELMAR ESTATE THE HOUSES ARE ALL UNDER 5 YEARS OLD. THEY ARE SITUATED PLEASANTLY. THEY ARE QUITE BIG AND HAVE NICE GARDENS. THE HOUSES ARE NOT JUST SEMI-DETACHED. BUT DETACHED AS WELL. THE BUILDING MATERIALS ARE ALL BRICKS BUT SOME OF THE BUNGALOW ROOFS ARE SLATES AND SOME TILES.ON SOME OF THE TERRACED HOUSES THERE ARE SOME WOOD PANELS.
